#	HDIC Project
#
#	Integrated Database of Hanzi Dictionaries in Early Japan
#
#	KTB_entries : Kozanjibon Tenrei Bansho Meigi database
#
#	Kozanjibon Tenrei Bansho Meigi 篆隷萬象名義, Kozanji copy 高山寺本.
#	monk Kukai of the Heian Period 空海, c. 827-835.
#	A Hanzi (Chinese character) dictionary.
#
#	Version: 1.3.2
#	Date: 25 September 1994
#	Last update : 30 April 2016
#
#	Copyright (c) 1994-2016 HDIC project, IKEDA Shoju (Chair)
#	LI Yuan (Person in Charge)
#	Department of Linguistic Sciences, Hokkaido University Graduate School of Letters
#	North 10, West 7, Kita-ku Sapporo, Hokkaido, 060-0810 Japan
#	Contact: hdic_info@let.hokudai.ac.jp
#
#	Feel free to copy and distribute.
#	Send bug reports and feature requests via email.
#
#	CSV Format information:
#	----------------------
#	TBID (v_wwwxyz) 	: Book(v), leaf(www), recto-verso(x), line(y) and number(z)
#	TB_vol_radical (xx#yyy)	: Volume(xx) and radical number(yyy)
#	TB_radical	: Radical of Chinese character 
#	Entry		: Headword
#	Entry_type	: For details, refer to the following section
#	Entry_diff	: Differences of transliteration with other scholars
#	Unicode		: Unicode scalar value
#	SYID (vwwwxyyyzz)	: Book(v), leaf(www), recto-verso(x), line(yy) and number(z)
#	YYID (Ywwxxxyy-z)	: Volume(ww), leaf(xxx), line(yy) and number(z)
#	TB_remarks	: Editor's notes
#
#	Entry_type:
#	----------
#	Regular		: 隷書(=楷書)掲出字
#	Regular-omitted		: 隷書掲出字脱
#	Seal_regular		: 篆書掲出字 + 隷書掲出字
#	Seal_regular-omitted	: 篆書掲出字, 隷書掲出字脱
#	Embedded_regular	: 埋字(隷書掲出字)
#	Embedded_seal_regular	: 埋字(篆書掲出字+隷書掲出字)
#	Embedded_regular-omitted	: 埋字(隷書掲出字脱)
#	Embedded_seal		: 埋字(篆書掲出字)
#	Embedded_omitted	: 埋字+脱字
#	Omitted				: 脱字
#	Songben Yupian		: 宋本《玉篇》増補之異体字
#
#	Abbreviations:
# 	-------------
#	TB	: Tenrei Bansho Meigi 篆隷万象名義, Kozanji copy 高山寺本
#	YY	: Yuanben Yupian 原本玉篇, fragments of vol.8, 9, 18, 19, 22, 24 and 27
#	SY	: Songben Yupian 宋本玉篇, Zecuntang edition 沢存堂本
#
# 	白	: Shirafuji's transliteration 
# 	宮	: Miyazawa's transliteration
#	上	: Ueda's transliteration
#	呂	: Lv's transliteration
#
#	References:
#	----------
#	Shirafuji	: Shirafuji Noriyuki 白藤禮幸, An Index of Headwords in the Tenrei Bansho Meigi 掲出字索引, Materials from Ancient Glossaries in the Kozanji Temple Collection 1 高山寺古辞書資料第一, Tokyo: Uiversity of Tokyo Press 東京大学出版会, 1977.
#	Miyazawa	: Miyazawa Toshimasa 宮澤俊雅, A List of Headwords with Notes in the Tenrei Bansho Meigi 掲出字一覧表, Materials from Ancient Glossaries in the Kozanji Temple Collection 1 高山寺古辞書資料第一, Tokyo: University of Tokyo Press 東京大学出版会, 1977.
#	Ueda		: Ueda Tadashi 上田正, A Complete List of Fanqie in the Original Yupian 玉篇反切総覧, Kobe: Private edition, 1986.
#	Lv		: Lv Hao 呂浩, Zhuanli Wanxiang Mingyi: A Transliteration and Text-critical Notes 篆隸萬象名義校釋, Shanghai: Xuelin Press 學林出版社, 2007.
#
#	This work was supported by JSPS KAKENHI Grant Number 25370506.
#
